'''金德训'''（{{kor|k=김덕훈|hj=金德訓|名=北}}，{{bd|1962年|||}}<ref>{{Cite web |script-title=ko:김덕훈(남성) |publisher=Ministry of Unification |work=nkinfo.unikorea.go.kr |access-date=21 March 2019 |url= http://nkinfo.unikorea.go.kr/nkp/theme/viewPeople_m.do?nkpmno=10302 |language=ko  }}</ref>），现任[[朝鲜总理列表|朝鲜内阁总理]]、[[朝鲜劳动党中央政治局|朝鲜劳动党中央政治局]]常委。2020年8月13日，经[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国国务委员会|朝鲜国务委员会]]提名后，被[[最高人民会议|最高人民会议]]常任委员会任命为总理，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20200814001600325?section=nk%2Fnk |title=N.K. leader warns against accepting outside assistance over flood damage due to virus risk |accessdate=2020-09-20 |archive-date=2020-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831000509/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20200814001600325?section=nk%2Fnk |dead-url=no }}</ref>他也是[[朝鲜劳动党中央委员会政治局常务委员会|朝鲜劳动党中央政治局常委]]。<ref>{{Cite web |title=North Korea's New Year's Eve party plenum reveals major leadership reshuffle |last=Kim |first=Jeongmin |work=NK News |date=1 January 2020 |access-date=2 January 2020 |url=https://www.nknews.org/2020/01/north-koreas-new-years-eve-party-plenum-reveals-major-leadership-reshuffle/ |archive-date=2020-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101181147/https://www.nknews.org/2020/01/north-koreas-new-years-eve-party-plenum-reveals-major-leadership-reshuffle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>曾任[[朝鲜内阁|朝鲜内阁]]副总理、[[朝鲜勞動黨中央委員會|朝鲜勞動黨中央委員會]]副委員長、朝鲜最高人民会议预算委员会委员长。在被最高人民会议任命为副总理之前，他曾是[[朝韩关系|朝韩合作事务]]特别代表。<ref>Grisafi, John G. "Former Delegate for North-South Cooperation Becomes Vice Premier." NK News North Korea News. North Korea News, 20 June 2014. Web. 20 Oct. 2015. Copy & paste citation</ref><ref>[http://kcna.co.jp/item/2014/201404/news09/20140409-36ee.html Fifth Cabinet Vice Premier Appointed, May 1, 2014] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413155508/http://www.kcna.co.jp/item/2014/201404/news09/20140409-36ee.html |date=April 13, 2014 }}</ref>

